{
  "chapter": 36,
  "chapter_summary": "史红英步入礼堂行刺帅孟雄，金逐流从匾额后飞出救援。史红英先以毒针刺中帅孟雄肩头，再以鞭剑双绝大闹礼堂。金逐流与史白都激烈交锋，打落沙千峰门牙示威，又突袭帅孟雄但未能擒住。院子里厉南星、公孙燕与贺大娘、安俊庭等人混战。厉南星斩断贺大娘双掌，公孙燕击杀郑雄图。连城虎见贺大娘已死，绝望自杀。李敦夫妇与安俊庭苦战。义军里应外合发起攻城，城中烟火信号四起。金逐流与史红英在史白都、文道庄、阳浩三大高手围攻下陷入苦战。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_nan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "厉南星",
      "listener": "char_li_dun",
      "text": "怎么办？",
      "tone": "焦急"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_dun",
      "speaker_name": "李敦",
      "listener": "char_li_nan_xing",
      "text": "只好见机行事吧！",
      "tone": "苦笑"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_jun_ting",
      "speaker_name": "安俊庭",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别打断这位姑娘的说书，照常的唱下去吧！",
      "tone": "平静"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_jun_ting",
      "speaker_name": "安俊庭",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位姑娘唱得很好，我要请她赏面，再给我唱一段红拂夜奔！",
      "tone": "微笑"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_cai_feng",
      "speaker_name": "何彩凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小女子唱得不好，大人谬赏了。",
      "tone": "平静"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_jun_ting",
      "speaker_name": "安俊庭",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，好！谁说她唱得不好？正因为她唱得太好了，所以我请她下来领赏！",
      "tone": "大笑"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_jun_ting",
      "speaker_name": "安俊庭",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是个大老粗，不解妙处，好在这里有个知音之人！连大人，还是你来说说她的好处吧，也好叫她们知道咱们是赏罚分明！",
      "tone": "调侃"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "speaker_name": "连城虎",
      "listener": "char_he_cai_feng",
      "text": "想不到在这里听到了山东的梨花大鼓，这是鼓书中的妙品啊！何姑娘，你混在川西的一个小班子里，不赚太委屈了自己吗？嘿嘿，哈哈！真人面前何必再说假话，快快随我进去领赏吧！",
      "tone": "大笑"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_jun_ting",
      "speaker_name": "安俊庭",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "乐老头，你这个班子里似乎多出一位姑娘，嘿嘿，就是这位姑娘！你叫她也一同下来领赏吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_cai_feng",
      "speaker_name": "何彩凤",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "text": "连大人，你要领赏，我就成全你吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "speaker_name": "公孙燕",
      "listener": "char_li_nan_xing",
      "text": "厉大哥，是你！",
      "tone": "欣喜"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_dun",
      "speaker_name": "李敦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "给我躺下吧！",
      "tone": "厉声"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_daniang",
      "speaker_name": "贺大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好呀，姓厉的小子，你居然还没有死，老娘就成全你们，让你们做个同命鸳鸯吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_nan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "厉南星",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小心，这妖妇爪上有毒！",
      "tone": "焦急"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_nan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "厉南星",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今日非切下你的毒爪不可！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "speaker_name": "公孙燕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叫你们知道姑娘的厉害！",
      "tone": "豪迈"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "speaker_name": "公孙燕",
      "listener": "char_he_daniang",
      "text": "老妖婆，你也吃我一剑！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "speaker_name": "公孙燕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不碍事，且让你们也看看我的夺剑功夫！",
      "tone": "自信"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "speaker_name": "公孙燕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以一换二，算来还是我占了便宜！",
      "tone": "得意"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "speaker_name": "公孙燕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在轮到你了，有本领的就再来夺剑吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_xiong_tu",
      "speaker_name": "郑雄图",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "text": "好丫头，我与你拼了！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_dun",
      "speaker_name": "李敦",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_hu",
      "text": "连大人，你可真是对得住朋友啊！你既然只要富贵功名，那我的解药也不能给你了。但我也不杀你，让你自己忏悔去吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_nan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "厉南星",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "text": "快去帮忙李大哥！",
      "tone": "焦急"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "speaker_name": "公孙燕",
      "listener": "char_li_nan_xing",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "认真"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_da_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "高大成",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "text": "你这小丫头也来欺我！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_jun_ting",
      "speaker_name": "安俊庭",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来人啦！",
      "tone": "焦急"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我是反了，我是不想活了。但这里最少有一个人要陪我死掉，他就是你所要巴结的帅孟雄！",
      "tone": "冷酷"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_meng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "帅孟雄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "区区一口毒针，谅它也还不能就要了我的性命。史姑娘，你扔掉兵器，赶快向客人赔罪，咱们还可商量。",
      "tone": "平静"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "speaker_name": "史白都",
      "listener": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "text": "你这贱丫头反了反了！你，你，你，你是不想活啦！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你敢上来！你要上来，陪我死的就不只一个了！",
      "tone": "冷酷"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "speaker_name": "史白都",
      "listener": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "text": "你的功夫是我教的，岂能在我面前逞强？哼，我为什么不敢上来？",
      "tone": "冷笑"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_meng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "帅孟雄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快快把贺大娘找回来！",
      "tone": "焦急"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "text": "有我保护你的小姐，你快走吧！",
      "tone": "认真"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "speaker_name": "史白都",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "好小子，你当真是胆大包大！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "text": "多承夸奖，好，这就请你看我虎口拔牙的手段！",
      "tone": "大笑"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "text": "史帮主，你看我虎口拔牙的下段如何？",
      "tone": "得意"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dao_zhuang",
      "speaker_name": "文道庄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金逐流休得逞能！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "text": "史帮主，我这虎口拔牙的手段，你要不要也尝一尝。",
      "tone": "调侃"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "speaker_name": "史白都",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "岂有此理，你这小子也敢来欺我？",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，射人先射马，擒贼先擒王！他中了我的毒针，不要让他有喘息的机会！",
      "tone": "激动"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dao_zhuang",
      "speaker_name": "文道庄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪里走！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "厉大哥在外面！",
      "tone": "欣喜"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_dong_shi_sanniang",
      "text": "臭婆娘，昨日饶了你的命，你展然还敢回来与我作对，要不要我再剥掉你的衣裳？",
      "tone": "嘲讽"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": "char_qing_fu_dao_ren",
      "text": "树倒猢狲散，我看你还是回去真正当道士的好！",
      "tone": "冷静"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_fu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青符道人",
      "listener": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "text": "多谢姑娘善言相劝。",
      "tone": "平静"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "speaker_name": "史白都",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "待我抓了这个丫头，再和你这牛鼻子算帐！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_fu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青符道人",
      "listener": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "text": "我是外人也不忍伤害史姑娘，你是哥哥，如要拿妹妹巴结权贵，我看不过眼，从今之后，各走各的路吧。我在三清观等你，但只怕你没找我算帐的机会了！",
      "tone": "认真"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "speaker_name": "史白都",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "即使西昌给你们的人攻破，城破之前，我也要取你这小子的性命！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dao_zhuang",
      "speaker_name": "文道庄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，无论如何，也不能放过他们！中儿，随我来报这一鞭之仇吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    }
  ],
